---
title: Component Interaction Flow
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Starfield as Starfield (Canvas)
    participant Window as Window Events
    participant StarModal as Star Modal
    participant HubbleData as /hubble/data.json

    Note over Starfield: Renders ~200 stars<br/>6 are "special" (gold)

    User->>Starfield: Click on golden star
    Starfield->>Starfield: Hit detection (20px radius)
    Starfield->>Window: dispatchEvent("starclick", {hubbleIndex})

    Note over StarModal: Loaded on page idle

    StarModal->>HubbleData: fetch("/hubble/data.json")
    HubbleData-->>StarModal: HubbleEntry[]

    Window->>StarModal: "starclick" event
    StarModal->>StarModal: setIsOpen(true), setEntry(data[index])
    StarModal->>User: Display modal with image + info

    User->>StarModal: Click close / Press Escape / Click backdrop
    StarModal->>StarModal: setIsOpen(false)
    StarModal->>User: Modal closes (AnimatePresence exit)

    Note over User,StarModal: Focus returns to<br/>previously focused element

    rect rgb(26,35,46)
        Note over Starfield: Astronaut Mascot Flow
        User->>User: Scroll to new section
        Note right of User: IntersectionObserver<br/>detects visible section
        Note right of User: Astronaut drifts<br/>toward active section
    end
